# Real watchlist data produced by tools/load-lists.js.
#
# Git-ignored on purpose: real lists are never published by accident. The public
# site ships the synthetic sample (lists/sample.js). To put real lists on the
# site you force-add this file deliberately — `git add -f lists/live.js` — after
# checking the source licences (OpenSanctions is CC-BY-NC; see SOURCES.md).
#
# The customer name you screen is never written here or anywhere: it is typed at
# runtime and matched in the browser.
lists/live.js
lists/live/
